1 - Write a lambda expression to implement Runnable and start a thread.

2 - Use Optional to avoid NullPointerException on a possibly null string.

3 - Create a CompletableFuture to run a task asynchronously and print result.

4 - Explain method reference for a static method and write code example.

5 - Implement Callable to return sum of first N numbers and use Future to get result.

6 - Write a program to chain multiple CompletableFuture tasks.

7 - Use method reference to an instance method of a particular object.

8 - Write a program that uses Optional.orElse() to provide default value.

9 - Explain difference between Future and CompletableFuture.

10 - Write a lambda expression for Comparator to sort objects by multiple fields.